Singing choirs of Charles University to be heard at the concert Students of Velvet
The combination of the celebrations of the International Day of Studence and the Anniversary of the Velvet Revolution with a musical experience is offered for the third time by the Festa Academica festival.
During it, he will present at twenty high school and undergraduate choirs.
The main focus of the festival is two concerts held on 17 November.
"The University of Karlovo has a large share in the festival."
