The patronage of the Mayor of the City of Prague, Bohuslav Svoboda, and the Rector of Charles University, Václav Hampl, took over the patronage of the event.
The festival will take place from 16 to 20 November in Prague and Pardubice.
In addition to ceremonial concerts, the timetable also offers a number of musical gatherings, a student happening, a matinee and other shows.
